dct_title_s: France--north coast, Berck to Boulogne-sur-Mer (Raster Image)
dct_description_sm: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "From a French chart of 1997." Place names in French, with glossary in English. "Soundings in meters." Includes tidal currents chart. Georeferenced nautical chart. Map no. 37106.
This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
